Historic climate data for a baseline period (1970–1998) and future projected data for 2071–2099 under the RCP8.5 scenario were obtained for southwestern England from the Coupled Model Intercomparison Project Phase 5 (CMIP5; 
 Taylor et al., 2012) as described by 
 Rose et al. (2015b). In order to calculate mean seasonal pasture contamination, there was no carry-over of infective larvae on pasture between years, and model output is presented as a mean of the 29  years simulated.
